citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:45 PM on 16-
May-2023. Inspectors attempted to contact the licensee by knocking on the door, calling the phone number on file and
leaving a voice message requesting a return call, and waited 30 minutes before departing.
Additional Inspectors:
Lauren Murphy, VETERINARY MEDICAL OFFICEREnd Section
